#define PREC (   REG)    REG##_INT, REG##_FRAC, REG##_SIGNED, #REG

Can be used to have shorter access to registers precisions using Module Config IMG_Fix_Clip() function.

#define PREC_C (   REG)    REG##_INT+ REG##_FRAC, REG##_SIGNED, #REG

Can be used to have shorter access to registers precisions using Module Config IMG_clip() function.
